-- KDB Financial Plans Share Sale in First Half of Next Year, Yonhap Says
-- Seonjin Cha
-- 2010-06-15T01:17:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/kdb-financial-plans-share-sale-in-first-half-of-next-year-yonhap-says.html

          
          
             KDB Financial Group Inc. is planning
to hold an initial public offering in the first half of next
year, Yonhap News reported, citing Chairman Min Euoo Sung.  
 Separately, KDB Financial will sell Daewoo Shipbuilding &
Marine Engineering Co. after completing its acquisition of
Daewoo Engineering & Construction Co., the Korean-language news
agency said today.  
 The state-run bank is planning a South Korean IPO in 2011,
a spokesman said by phone today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Shinhye Kang in Seoul at 
 skang24@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        